dcterms:creator: L. F. Wightman
dcterms:description: The Law School Admission Dataset includes information on 21,790 law students studying in 163 different law schools across the United States, containing entrance exam scores (LSAT), grade-point average (GPA) prior to law school, and the first year average grade (FYA).
dcterms:title: Law School Admission Dataset

dcterms:creator: R. Kohavi
dcterms:description: The Adult Income Dataset contains information on 48,842 individuals, with 14 features including age, education, race, etc., used to predict whether an individual's income exceeds $50K.
dcterms:title: Adult Income Dataset
